                                    <p>
                                        <locus from="2r" to="2r" scheme="folios"/>: Opening plain initial G over 3 lines in red. </p>
                                    <p>
                                        <locus from="2r" to="53r" scheme="folios"/>: plain initials over 2 lines in red. On <locus from="45v" to="49r" scheme="folios"/> the initals are written in green. <locus from="19v" to="19v" scheme="folios"/>: flourish in red added to the last initial on the page. </p>
                                    <p>
                                        <locus from="34v" to="34v" scheme="folios"/>: initial outlined in black in, filled with red and black. </p>
                                    <p>
